		<title>扬琴</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.chinacno.org/knowledges/instruments/弹/197-扬琴"/>
		<published>2011-11-27T03:45:03+00:00</published>
		<updated>2011-11-27T03:45:03+00:00</updated>
		<id>http://www.chinacno.org/knowledges/instruments/弹/197-扬琴</id>
		<author>
			<name>肖文礼</name>
			<email>xiaowenli@chinacno.org</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;
	击弦乐器。又名洋琴、打琴。广泛应用于民歌、戏曲、曲艺伴奏，也用于器乐合奏和独奏。&lt;/p&gt;
</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;
	击弦乐器。又名洋琴、打琴。广泛应用于民歌、戏曲、曲艺伴奏，也用于器乐合奏和独奏。&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
